{"lemma":"جَنَّةٌ","slug":"جَنَّةٌ","root":"ج.ن.ن","root_slug":"ج-ن-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ن-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَنَّة","root":"جنن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":147},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6380"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"garden"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"paradise, heaven, the Paradise, the Heaven, Elysium"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جُنَّ (junna)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"madness, craziness, possession, mania"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a jinn, demon, genie","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"jinn, demons, genies","tags":["Classical","plural","plural-only"],"examples":[{"text":"مِنَ ٱلْجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","english":"from among the jinn/demons and Men."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thing which veils, conceals, hides, covers, or protects"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"weapon or armor, a thing used to protect oneself, anything protective or defensive"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"piece of cloth which a woman wears covering the face and the two sides of the bosom, a type of hijab or veil"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Inherited from Proto-Semitic, the sense of a paradise being borrowed from Classical Syriac ܓܰܢܬܳܐ (gannəṯā). Compare Hebrew גַּן (gan), Aramaic גִּנָּא (ginnā), Ugaritic 𐎂𐎐 (gn). Synchronically, related to جَنّ (jann, “covering, protecting”)"},"ipa":["/d͡ʒan.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6380","headword_ar":"جَنَّةٌ","root":"jn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garden, such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busotaAn","text_ar":"بُسْتَان"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walled garden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadiyqap","text_ar":"حَدِيقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palm-trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palms and other trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"if containing palm-trees and grape-vines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"otherwise, if containing trees, called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hdyqp","text_ar":"حديقة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Aboo-'Alee in the Tedhkireh, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bstAn","text_ar":"بستان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having trees by which the ground is concealed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealing trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tall palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shadowing trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the tangling, or luxuriousness of their branches; as though concealing at once what is beneath them: then"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bstAn","text_ar":"بستان"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because of its dense and shadowing trees: (Bd in ii. 23:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bstAn","text_ar":"بستان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palms and other trees, dense, and shadowing by the tangling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"luxuriousness, and denseness, of their branches;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were originally the inf. n. of un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~ahu","text_ar":"جَنَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and meaning “ a single act of veiling ” or “ concealing ” &c.: (Ksh ib.:) then, with the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paradise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the abode of recompense;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinaAn","text_ar":"جِنَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"therein; (Ksh and Bd ib.;) or because the various delights prepared therein for mankind are concealed in the present state of existence: (Bd ib.:) [and] hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljan~aAtu","text_ar":"الجَنَّاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gardens"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Paradise], (so in a copy of the S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~aAtu EadonK","text_ar":"جَنَّاتُ عَدْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gardens of continual abode"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (so in another copy of the S:) [for] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~apN","text_ar":"جَنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajin~apN","text_ar":"اَجِنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinayonap","text_ar":"جِنَيْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~apN","text_ar":"جُنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this last is strange. (MF, TA.) [Dim. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junayonapN","text_ar":"جُنَيْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", vulgarly pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinayonap","text_ar":"جِنَيْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A garden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little Paradise."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AC%D9%86%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"جنة الأرواح","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_22","lexicon_en":"Al-Munāwī, al-Tawqīf ʿalā Muhimmāt al-Taʿārīf (d. 1622 CE)","lexicon_ar":"التوقيف على مهمات التعاريف للمناوي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=36484#8007f4","body_html":"<span>جنة الأرواح: تنويرها بحقائق العلم في حضرة الشهود الأقدس.</span><br>"}]}}